# ─── Secrets & local credentials (NEVER commit) ───
**/.env
**/.auth
.uipath/.auth
# UiPath local-run overwrites carry real tenant/connection/folder IDs
**/__uipath/*
!**/__uipath/uipath.json.example
**/.uipath/

# ─── Private working notes (contain tenant/connection IDs) ───
HANDOFF.md
SESSION_CONTEXT.md

# ─── Local run outputs / eval artifacts ───
**/notify_out.json
**/eval-results.json
**/out*.json
**/sample_*.json

# ─── Python / coded-agent envs (regenerate with `uip codedagent setup`) ───
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc

# ─── Node / web app (regenerate with `npm install` / `npm run build`) ───
**/node_modules/
**/dist/

# ─── Build output (regenerate with `uip solution pack`) ───
build/
*.nupkg
# The packed Case nupkg embeds a Stripe key — ship only the scrubbed unpacked source
MaestroCase/_package_download/

# ─── Source decks / reference material (not code) ───
*.pptx
*.tex
AgentHack_Reimbursement_Plan.pdf
*.png

# ─── OS / editor junk ───
.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
